BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-06T03:30:00&endDate=2026-04-07T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nBAKERLOO LINE: Easter Monday\, 6 April\, no service between Stonebridge Park and Harrow & Wealdstone. There will also be no LIONESS LINE service between Willesden Junction and Watford Junction\, LONDON NORTHWESTERN trains will not call at Euston or Harrow & Wealdstone\, and SOUTHERN trains will not call at Wembley Central or Harrow & Wealdstone. Special bus service 718 operates between Stonebridge Park and Harrow & Wealdstone via Wembley High Road (Park Lane)\, Wembley Central\, North Wembley\, Preston Road (for Metropolitan line and bus route 223 to/from South Kenton) and Kenton.
